{
  "stem": "27.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Now, can you imagine, they hang a person and you have to stand there like-- [CRYING] how, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Isn't it terrible?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But I didn't feel that, which is unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Can you imagine feeling glad that a father who begs for his son's life, the son has to hang him?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Just beyond any comprehension, beyond any human understanding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going back and forth, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, but you understand how your mind works.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Longwy, they almost eliminated, I would say 80% of the so-called 500 engineers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then as we went on to Longwy, I told you, so they stopped the train in Ulm, and there was the death march.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would say 150 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Took us three weeks, and we slept always on the side of the road in a forest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They give us a little hot water in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's all they had, and they give us a little bread and a little soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's all it was, very little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were really starving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, but I want to tell you something about starvation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first day's bad, the second day is very bad, the third day is better, and after the fourth day, it's nothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You don't feel any pain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But thirst, that's the pain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the killer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, we didn't have any-- the last five days, you know, we didn't have any water, any food, zero, zero, nothing and the thirst was a killer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But people eat, you know, worms, anything they find.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could not eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember one guy came to me, I found three, have one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's no way in the world I could have eaten it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No way and they-- it's a luxury you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He meant it well.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
